/wp.me\/p95VHY-2vV","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":20786,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/07\/30\/deen-dawah-world\/","url_meta":{"origin":9667,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Islam: Religion of Islam to reach everywhere in the world","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 30, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Tamim al-Dari reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThis matter will certainly reach every place touched by the night and day. Allah will not leave a house or residence but that Allah will cause this religion to enter it, by which the honorable will\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27043,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/01\/16\/pleased-allah-muhammad-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":9667,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Dua: I am pleased with Allah, Muhammad, Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 16, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Thawban reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever says when he enters the evening, \u2018I am pleased with Allah as a Lord, with Islam as a religion, and with Muhammad as a prophet,\u2019 it will be a duty upon Allah to please him.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":10201,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/12\/11\/islam-vast-enter-gently\/","url_meta":{"origin":9667,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Islam: This religion is vast, so embrace it with gentleness","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 11, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, this religion is firmly solid, so come into it gently.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 13052 Grade: Hasan\u00a0(fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u0646 \u0623\u0646\u0633 \u0628\u0646 \u0645\u0627\u0644\u0643 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0647\u064e\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u0627\u0644\u062f\u0650\u0651\u064a\u0646\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37655,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/01\/19\/dua-tawhid-ibrahim\/","url_meta":{"origin":9667,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplication upon monotheism, morning and evening","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 19, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Ubayy ibn Ka\u2019b reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, taught us to say when we entered the morning, \u201cWe have entered the morning upon the pure nature of Islam, the word of sincerity, the Sunnah of our Prophet Muhammad, peace and blessings be upon him,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24961,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/06\/05\/allah-turns-heart-how-wills\/","url_meta":{"origin":9667,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Hearts: O Allah, keep my heart steadfast upon Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 5, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would often say, \u201cO Turner of the hearts, keep my heart firm upon Your religion!\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2140 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u064a\u064f\u0643\u0652\u062b\u0650\u0631\u064f \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u064a\u064e\u0642\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3412,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/06\/22\/embrace-islam-even-if-dislike-it\/","url_meta":{"origin":9667,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Islam: Embrace Islam, even if you dislike it","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 22, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said to a man, \u201cEmbrace Islam.\u201d The man said, \u201cI find that I dislike it.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cEmbrace Islam, even if you dislike it.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 12061 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/9667","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=9667"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/9667\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=9667"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=9667"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=9667"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}